.Dd Nov 12, 2025
.Dt querydbs
.Os Linux
.Sh NAME
.Nm querydbs
.Nd Query a set of database files with a common schema
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op options
table_name
SQL
db
[db ...]

.Sh DESCRIPTION
Run an SQL query against output databases from
.Xr gufi_query 1 . Given output database file names, the program will union the tables from each of the database files into a view named v<table_name>.

.Sh OPTIONS
.Bl -tag -width -indent
.It Fl h, -help
help
.It Fl d\ <delim>
delimiter
.It Fl -attach-prefix
name when attaching dbs
.It Fl -verbose, V
Show the equivalent shell command passing raw SQL into gufi_sqlite3
.El

.Sh EXIT STATUS
.Bl -tag -width -indent
.It EXIT_SUCCESS or EXIT_FAILURE
.El

.Pp
.Sh FILES
.Bl -tag -width -compact
.It querydbs
.El

\# .Sh BUGS
\# .Sh EXAMPLE
\# .Sh FLOW

.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr gufi_sqlite3 1
